Package: td
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fast terminal task manager
 td is a lightweight terminal task manager written in Go and backed by SQLite.
 It supports priorities, projects, recurring tasks, due dates, search,
 statistics, and SQLite persistence.